+## Requirements
+
+### Build Requirements
+
+- OpenSSL 3.0+ development headers
+- Automake, Autoconf, Libtool
+- GCC or Clang with C99 support
+- pkg-config
+
+### Runtime Requirements
+
+- OpenSSL 3.0+ libraries
+- Linux kernel 4.0+ (for modern crypto)
+
